## What You Get

**20 AI Tools in 6 Categories:**

| Category | What It Does |
|----------|-------------|
| ğŸ” Search | Find existing code, check if features exist |
| ğŸ“ Context | Understand files, track changes, remember decisions |
| ğŸ”— Dependencies | See what imports what, visualize structure |
| ğŸ“Š Analysis | Code quality metrics, config auditing |
| âš ï¸ Safety | Check breaking changes before refactoring |
| ğŸ—‚ï¸ Management | Index files, find TODOs, git history |

---

## How It Works

**You ask naturally:**
```
"Add authentication"
```

**Copilot automatically:**
1. Searches existing code
2. Finds `src/auth/jwt.py`
3. Suggests modifying it instead of creating new files

**No explicit tool calls needed!**

